<Document>
  <name>11122 274th Ave NW — parcel, setbacks, South &amp; North options</name>
  <description>PIN 30-00481-0115 — Sherburne GIS parcel + modeled setbacks + two build options (South 32×40 pad + straight driveway; North 40×32 + L-drive if that scan ran). Open in Google My Maps (Create map → Import) or Google Earth; on your phone open the same map in the Google Maps app with Location on for live GPS vs the layers. Setbacks are planning offsets (67′ S/E, 25′ N, 10′ W) — verify with Livonia Township and a survey.</description>
